[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/thunder_wave">Thunder Wave</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/thunder_wave">Thunder Wave</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>A weak electric charge is launched at the foe. It causes paralysis if it hits.</p>